                    <h3>ONLINE TEXT BOOKS, NOTEBOOKS AND QUESTION PAPERS</h3>
                    <p>To score high in any exam students first need to master the textbooks. Students who want to gain command over the subjects must solve all the questions of the textbooks. Here we have compiled the Textbook Solutions for CBSE, ICSE and State Boards.</p>
                    <p>Solving all the questions of the textbook without any trouble is a difficult task for students. Most of the time, they get stuck with particular question. Here, Textbook solutions play an important role by helping them in understanding the method of solving the question. It not just helps in their studies but also gives them a new approach to solve the questions in the easiest way.</p>
                    <p>CBSE and many state boards are now following the NCERT textbooks for classes 1 to 12 in their school course curriculum. Not only these, for various competitive examinations like IIT, NEET, UPSC, etc; it is being recommended to refer to the NCERT book. This is because the content in the textbook is developed in a simpler and easily understandable way. One can start from basics and can go to the higher level by studying through these books.</p>
                    <p>NCERT provides various study resources to the students studying in different classes. Going through these study resources without fail helps the students in understanding the details of the course, enabling them to be prepared throughout the academic year. Also, it develops educational kits and multimedia digital materials to help students with their studies. Exam preparation, without a doubt, is much more convenient with these NCERT resources.</p>

